      <div class="msgContentFrame">I put myself as /afk when I don't want to be bothered. As such, if random people are trying to whisper me, then I don't reply... because I don't want to be bothered.  <br /> <br />Mining bots though usually find a way to hack the system to get the ore. For example, flying under the map, flying at ridiculous speeds, etc. It happens on probably all servers people just don't pay attention. Those that do just report said player as a bot and go on their merry ways. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm"><span style="color:Gold">Aresella the Kingslayer - 80 Combat Rogue</span> ~^~ <span style="color:pink">Vyerix - 80 Prot Paladin</span> ~^~ <span style="color:Mediumblue">Aislynn - 80 Resto Shaman</span> ~^~ <span style="color:Orange">Araxi - 80 Balance Druid</span> ~^~ <span style="color:Lavender">Alaxandra - 80 Shadow Priest</span> ~^~ <span style="color:brown">Alazara - 80 Prot Warrior</span> ~^~ <span style="color:Green">Xeliara - 70 BM Hunter</span> ~^~ <span style="color:Aqua">GÃ­zmo - Goblin</span> ~^~ <span style="color:brown">Faewyn - Worgen</span></span></div></div>
